oc:kn_16f129ac a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When scaffolding any plugin" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The plugin.json manifest MUST be in the .claude-plugin/ directory at plugin root. All component directories (commands, agents, skills, hooks) MUST be at plugin root level, NOT nested inside .claude-plugin/." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Claude Code's auto-discovery scans specific locations; misplaced files will not be found." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_3d40a566 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When organizing plugin directory structure" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never place component directories (commands, agents, skills, hooks) inside .claude-plugin/. Do not name skill files anything other than SKILL.md. Do not use absolute paths or omit ./ prefix in manifest path fields." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These cause auto-discovery failures and path resolution errors that are hard to diagnose." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_47c14fc2 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When designing a new plugin's structure" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Start with the minimal plugin pattern (manifest + one command). Keep plugin.json lean — only specify custom paths when necessary. Rely on auto-discovery for standard layouts. Group related components together. Only create directories for components the plugin actually uses." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Minimizing configuration reduces errors. Auto-discovery handles standard layouts reliably. Over-structuring a small plugin adds maintenance burden." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_65e3ef35 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When naming any plugin component or configuring manifest paths" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use kebab-case for all directory and file names. Plugin names must be kebab-case, unique, lowercase with hyphens, no spaces or special characters. Custom paths in plugin.json supplement defaults — they do not replace them." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Consistent naming prevents conflicts and ensures auto-discovery works correctly. Supplementing defaults allows flexible organization without breaking conventions." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_7557b45c a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before publishing or distributing a plugin" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Before considering a plugin complete: verify plugin.json is in .claude-plugin/, verify component files have correct extensions (.md for commands/agents, SKILL.md for skills), verify YAML frontmatter syntax, verify all paths use ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}, verify referenced files exist." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Most plugin loading failures are caused by misplaced files, incorrect naming, or missing frontmatter." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_a788cf70 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When referencing any file path within hooks, MCP servers, scripts, or component files" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT} for all intra-plugin path references. Never use hardcoded absolute paths, relative paths from working directory, or home directory shortcuts." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Plugins install in different locations depending on installation method, OS, and user preferences. Portable paths ensure compatibility." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_dc307446 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring plugin.json path fields or naming the plugin" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Manifest paths must be relative to plugin root, start with ./, cannot use ../  or absolute paths, support arrays for multiple locations, and use forward slashes only (even on Windows). Plugin name must match regex: /^[a-z][a-z0-9]*(-[a-z0-9]+)*$/" ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are enforced by Claude Code's manifest validation. Invalid formats cause plugin load failures." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_fd6ab257 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:RecoveryTactic ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When troubleshooting plugin loading or discovery issues" ;
    oc:directiveContent "If components not loading: verify file location/extension, check YAML frontmatter syntax, ensure skills use SKILL.md not README.md. If path errors: replace hardcoded paths with ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}, verify paths start with ./. If auto-discovery fails: confirm directories at plugin root (not in .claude-plugin/), check kebab-case naming, restart Claude Code." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These cover the most common plugin configuration errors with their direct fixes." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

